For AFKing there if you dont have an epic, fire is probably the best because it will have its good DS on even when you are AFK, and as someone mention, it is immune to the wizzies fire nukes.  Anyway, I never tried AFKing there, but im sure it is possible, but wont be completly safe unless you have the epic. <p><table border="0">
