After reading the whole post in here, we can say that pet soloing is not really a problem, but there still is a little risk : <br>
.. pet can be killed<br>
.. wizz can fly to bridge and get help from guard if you are KOS to them (I am)<br>
.. if you go LD you are in trouble : because you are AFK, when you come back, you'll have to get help to log in without being killed<br>
<br>
<br>
now, of course, if you can really let pet fight all night while you are sleeping (or other activities, that's not my problem, up to you) it can be a worth taking risk (i don't know if VI would think it is an exploit)<br>
